info: Rating, 5 stars,  · February 2023,  · Stayed about a week
rating_comment:
We had an amazing time at SUFIA HOUSE-B2. The location was perfect - just a short Distance from all the shops and restaurants, but still quiet and peaceful. The apartment was clean, spacious and had all the amenities we needed, including a well-equipped kitchen.
But the real highlight of our trip was our host. They were incredibly friendly and accommodating, and went above and beyond to make sure we had a wonderful time. They provided us with great recommendations for local restaurants and sights, and were always available to answer any questions we had.
We truly felt at home during our stay, and we can't thank Host enough for their hospitality. We highly recommend Sufia House B2 and would love to stay here again in the future. Thank you for a fantastic experience!"
